<section xml:id="_md__s_e_c_u_r_i_t_y_1autotoc_md15">
<title>Reporting a Vulnerability</title>

<para>Security related findings should be reported under the repo Security Issues. Findings Risk scores will follow CVSS 3.x standard of scoring. Confirmed findings will be mitigated/remediated by risk level, within the respectful timeline listed below:</para>

<para><informaltable frame="all">
    <tgroup cols="2" align="left" colsep="1" rowsep="1">
      <colspec colname='c1'/>
      <colspec colname='c2'/>
<thead>
      <row  class='markdownTableHead'>
<entry>
<para>Risk   </para>
</entry><entry>
<para>Days    </para>
</entry></row>
</thead><tbody>
      <row  class='markdownTableRowOdd'>
<entry>
<para>Critical   </para>
</entry><entry>
<para>7    </para>
</entry></row>
      <row  class='markdownTableRowEven'>
<entry>
<para>High   </para>
</entry><entry>
<para>30    </para>
</entry></row>
      <row  class='markdownTableRowOdd'>
<entry>
<para>Medium   </para>
</entry><entry>
<para>60    </para>
</entry></row>
      <row  class='markdownTableRowEven'>
<entry>
<para>Low   </para>
</entry><entry>
<para>*   </para>
</entry></row>
    </tbody>
    </tgroup>
</informaltable>
</para>

<para>**Low findings fixes are discretionary* </para>
